{
  "name": "WF1 — Mercado Pago Webhook Central",
  "meta": { "templateId": "grind-wf1", "description": "Recibe IPN de Mercado Pago. Verifica firma HMAC. Enruta a Flujo SaaS (activa gym) o Flujo Tenant (procesa venta B2C: orders, créditos, CFDI, FitCoins, WhatsApp). Maqueta lista — solo agrega credenciales." },
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "sticky-legend",
      "name": "📋 INSTRUCCIONES",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [0, -200],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## WF1 — Mercado Pago Webhook Central\n\n**Credenciales requeridas:**\n1. `Supabase Grind` — URL + Service Role Key\n2. `MERCADO_PAGO_WEBHOOK_SECRET` — Variables de entorno n8n\n3. `TAX_PROVIDER_API_KEY` — Variables de entorno n8n\n4. `WHATSAPP_TOKEN` + `WHATSAPP_PHONE_ID` — Variables de entorno n8n\n\n**Cómo activar:**\n1. Agrega las credenciales en n8n → Credentials\n2. Configura las variables de entorno en n8n Settings\n3. Copia la URL del Webhook Trigger\n4. Pégala como `N8N_WEBHOOK_MP_URL` en tu `.env` del proyecto\n5. Activa el workflow\n\n**URL del Webhook:**\nhttps://aop00.app.n8n.cloud/webhook/grind-mp-ipn",
        "height": 280,
        "width": 500
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n1",
      "name": "🔵 Webhook: MP IPN",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [560, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "grind-mp-ipn",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": { "rawBody": true }
      },
      "webhookId": "grind-mp-ipn"
    },
    {
      "id": "n2",
      "name": "🔐 Verificar Firma HMAC",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [780, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const xSignature = $input.first().headers['x-signature'] || '';\nconst xRequestId = $input.first().headers['x-request-id'] || '';\nconst rawBody = $input.first().body;\nconst secret = $env['MERCADO_PAGO_WEBHOOK_SECRET'];\n\n// DEV: skip if no secret configured\nif (!secret) {\n  return [{ json: { valid: true, body: JSON.parse(rawBody || '{}'), xRequestId } }];\n}\n\nconst ts = (xSignature.match(/ts=(\\d+)/) || [])[1];\nconst v1 = (xSignature.match(/v1=([^,]+)/) || [])[1];\n\nif (!ts || !v1) {\n  return [{ json: { valid: false, reason: 'Missing ts or v1' } }];\n}\n\nlet parsedBody;\ntry { parsedBody = JSON.parse(rawBody || '{}'); } catch { parsedBody = {}; }\n\nconst dataId = parsedBody?.data?.id ?? '';\nconst manifest = `id:${dataId};request-id:${xRequestId};ts:${ts};`;\n\nconst crypto = require('crypto');\nconst computed = crypto.createHmac('sha256', secret).update(manifest).digest('base64');\nconst valid = computed === v1;\n\nreturn [{ json: { valid, body: parsedBody, xRequestId, manifest } }];"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n3",
      "name": "IF: Firma válida?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1000, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": { "caseSensitive": true, "leftValue": "", "typeValidation": "strict" },
          "conditions": [{ "leftValue": "={{ $json.valid }}", "rightValue": true, "operator": { "type": "boolean", "operation": "equals" } }],
          "combinator": "and"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n4-reject",
      "name": "❌ Responder 401",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [1000, 480],
      "parameters": {
        "respondWith": "text",
        "responseBody": "Unauthorized",
        "options": { "responseCode": 401 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n5",
      "name": "IF: type == payment?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1220, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "conditions": [{ "leftValue": "={{ $json.body.type }}", "rightValue": "payment", "operator": { "type": "string", "operation": "equals" } }],
          "combinator": "and"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n6-ignore",
      "name": "✅ OK (ignorar)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [1220, 480],
      "parameters": { "respondWith": "text", "responseBody": "OK", "options": { "responseCode": 200 } }
    },
    {
      "id": "n7",
      "name": "🌐 Fetch Payment de MP",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [1440, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "=https://api.mercadopago.com/v1/payments/{{ $json.body.data.id }}",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "httpHeaderAuth",
        "options": {},
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [{ "name": "Authorization", "value": "=Bearer {{ $env['MERCADO_PAGO_ACCESS_TOKEN_SAAS'] }}" }]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n8",
      "name": "IF: status == approved?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1660, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "conditions": [{ "leftValue": "={{ $json.status }}", "rightValue": "approved", "operator": { "type": "string", "operation": "equals" } }],
          "combinator": "and"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n9",
      "name": "🔍 Parsear external_reference",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1880, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const ref = $json.external_reference || '';\nconst paymentId = String($json.id);\nconst amount = $json.transaction_amount;\nconst payerEmail = $json.payer?.email || null;\n\nconst flowMatch  = ref.match(/flow:(saas|tenant)/);\nconst userMatch  = ref.match(/user:([^:]+)/);\nconst gymMatch   = ref.match(/gym:([^:]+)/);\n\nif (!flowMatch || !userMatch) {\n  throw new Error('No se puede parsear external_reference: ' + ref);\n}\n\nreturn [{ json: {\n  flowType: flowMatch[1],\n  userId:   userMatch[1],\n  gymId:    gymMatch?.[1] || null,\n  paymentId,\n  amount,\n  payerEmail\n} }];"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n10",
      "name": "🔀 Switch: SaaS vs Tenant",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.switch",
      "typeVersion": 3,
      "position": [2100, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "mode": "rules",
        "rules": {
          "values": [
            { "conditions": { "conditions": [{ "leftValue": "={{ $json.flowType }}", "rightValue": "saas", "operator": { "type": "string", "operation": "equals" } }], "combinator": "and" }, "outputKey": "SaaS" },
            { "conditions": { "conditions": [{ "leftValue": "={{ $json.flowType }}", "rightValue": "tenant", "operator": { "type": "string", "operation": "equals" } }], "combinator": "and" }, "outputKey": "Tenant" }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n11-saas",
      "name": "🏢 [SaaS] Activar Plan en gyms",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [2320, 160],
      "credentials": { "supabaseApi": { "name": "Supabase Grind ← AGREGAR CREDENCIAL" } },
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "update",
        "tableId": "gyms",
        "filterType": "string",
        "filterString": "owner_id=eq.{{ $json.userId }}",
        "dataToSend": "defineBelow",
        "fieldsUi": {
          "fieldValues": [
            { "fieldId": "plan_status", "fieldValue": "active" },
            { "fieldId": "saas_mp_payment_id", "fieldValue": "={{ $json.paymentId }}" },
            { "fieldId": "updated_at", "fieldValue": "={{ new Date().toISOString() }}" }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n12-tenant",
      "name": "📦 [Tenant] UPDATE orders → paid",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [2320, 440],
      "credentials": { "supabaseApi": { "name": "Supabase Grind ← AGREGAR CREDENCIAL" } },
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "update",
        "tableId": "orders",
        "filterType": "string",
        "filterString": "user_id=eq.{{ $json.userId }}&gym_id=eq.{{ $json.gymId }}&status=eq.pending",
        "dataToSend": "defineBelow",
        "fieldsUi": {
          "fieldValues": [
            { "fieldId": "status", "fieldValue": "paid" },
            { "fieldId": "mp_payment_id", "fieldValue": "={{ $json.paymentId }}" },
            { "fieldId": "updated_at", "fieldValue": "={{ new Date().toISOString() }}" }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n13-gymdata",
      "name": "🏋️ GET gym config (features, fiscal)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [2540, 440],
      "credentials": { "supabaseApi": { "name": "Supabase Grind ← AGREGAR CREDENCIAL" } },
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "getAll",
        "tableId": "gyms",
        "filterType": "string",
        "filterString": "id=eq.{{ $('n9').item.json.gymId }}",
        "limit": 1,
        "returnAll": false
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n14-fiscal",
      "name": "IF: fiscal habilitado?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [2760, 440],
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "conditions": [{ "leftValue": "={{ $json.features?.fiscal }}", "rightValue": true, "operator": { "type": "boolean", "operation": "equals" } }],
          "combinator": "and"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n15-cfdi",
      "name": "🧾 Emitir CFDI / Factura",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [2980, 340],
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "={{ $env['CFDI_WEBHOOK_URL'] || 'https://TU-PROVEEDOR-PAC.mx/cfdi/emit' }}",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [{ "name": "Authorization", "value": "=Bearer {{ $env['TAX_PROVIDER_API_KEY'] }}" }]
        },
        "sendBody": true,
        "contentType": "json",
        "bodyParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            { "name": "reference_id", "value": "={{ $('n12-tenant').item.json.id }}" },
            { "name": "customer_email", "value": "={{ $('n9').item.json.payerEmail }}" },
            { "name": "total", "value": "={{ $('n9').item.json.amount }}" },
            { "name": "tax_region", "value": "={{ $('n13-gymdata').item.json.tax_region }}" },
            { "name": "rfc", "value": "={{ $('n13-gymdata').item.json.rfc }}" },
            { "name": "description", "value": "Servicios de fitness Grind Project" }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n16-invoice",
      "name": "💾 INSERT invoice en Supabase",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [3200, 340],
      "credentials": { "supabaseApi": { "name": "Supabase Grind ← AGREGAR CREDENCIAL" } },
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "create",
        "tableId": "invoices",
        "dataToSend": "defineBelow",
        "fieldsUi": {
          "fieldValues": [
            { "fieldId": "order_id", "value": "={{ $('n12-tenant').item.json.id }}" },
            { "fieldId": "gym_id", "value": "={{ $('n9').item.json.gymId }}" },
            { "fieldId": "user_id", "value": "={{ $('n9').item.json.userId }}" },
            { "fieldId": "status", "value": "=={{ $json.success ? 'issued' : 'error' }}" },
            { "fieldId": "cfdi_uuid", "value": "={{ $json.uuid || null }}" },
            { "fieldId": "pdf_url", "value": "={{ $json.pdf_url || null }}" },
            { "fieldId": "xml_url", "value": "={{ $json.xml_url || null }}" },
            { "fieldId": "total", "value": "={{ $('n9').item.json.amount }}" },
            { "fieldId": "issued_at", "value": "={{ new Date().toISOString() }}" }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n17-fitcoins",
      "name": "🪙 INSERT FitCoins (+1 por $10)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [3200, 540],
      "credentials": { "supabaseApi": { "name": "Supabase Grind ← AGREGAR CREDENCIAL" } },
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "create",
        "tableId": "fitcoins",
        "dataToSend": "defineBelow",
        "fieldsUi": {
          "fieldValues": [
            { "fieldId": "gym_id", "value": "={{ $('n9').item.json.gymId }}" },
            { "fieldId": "user_id", "value": "={{ $('n9').item.json.userId }}" },
            { "fieldId": "amount", "value": "={{ Math.floor($('n9').item.json.amount / 10) }}" },
            { "fieldId": "source", "value": "purchase" },
            { "fieldId": "description", "value": "=Compra +{{ Math.floor($('n9').item.json.amount / 10) }} FitCoins" }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n18-whatsapp",
      "name": "📱 WhatsApp: Pago confirmado",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [3420, 440],
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "=https://graph.facebook.com/v18.0/{{ $env['WHATSAPP_PHONE_ID'] }}/messages",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [{ "name": "Authorization", "value": "=Bearer {{ $env['WHATSAPP_TOKEN'] }}" }]
        },
        "sendBody": true,
        "contentType": "json",
        "bodyParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            { "name": "messaging_product", "value": "whatsapp" },
            { "name": "to", "value": "=52{{ $env['TEST_WHATSAPP_PHONE'] }}" },
            { "name": "type", "value": "text" },
            { "name": "text", "value": "={ \"body\": \"✅ ¡Pago confirmado! ${{ $('n9').item.json.amount }} MXN recibido. Ya puedes reservar tus clases en Grind Project 💪\" }" }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n19-ok",
      "name": "✅ Respond 200 OK",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [3640, 440],
      "parameters": { "respondWith": "text", "responseBody": "OK", "options": { "responseCode": 200 } }
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "🔵 Webhook: MP IPN":               { "main": [[{ "node": "🔐 Verificar Firma HMAC",        "type": "main", "index": 0 }]] },
    "🔐 Verificar Firma HMAC":           { "main": [[{ "node": "IF: Firma válida?",               "type": "main", "index": 0 }]] },
